            <title>[SQL] REFERENCES 外來鍵的用法(含範例與mysql)</title>
            <link>http://localhost:1313/2022/03/01/sql-references-%E5%A4%96%E4%BE%86%E9%8D%B5%E7%9A%84%E7%94%A8%E6%B3%95%E5%90%AB%E7%AF%84%E4%BE%8B%E8%88%87mysql/</link>
